::Perndabot/FZ::

The door to the bridge opens and Perndabot walks in, nodding to
Wolfgang as he recognizes him. He then looks at FZ.

"I found this female on the mainland. She wants to talk to you." He
steps aside, gesturing toward Antagony.


--- In nbwrpg@y..., "Jen D." <jeniff@h...> wrote:
> Antagony smiled and followed. It wasn't too much a problem for her
if she 
> distracted Perndabot from duty. She was sure that he could
accomplish 
> anything he might have not done when he got back. She went over in
her mind 
> what the meeting with Zardus would be like, because her unusual
talent made 
> it possible to see into the future.
